{"id": "155015", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=155015", "title": "Glove of Sanguine Swiftblade", "text": "Glove of Sanguine Swiftblade is a unique &lt;a href=\"right%20glove\"&gt;right glove&lt;/a&gt; that was created by the &lt;a href=\"Daedric%20Prince\"&gt;Daedric Prince&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sanguine\"&gt;Sanguine&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=\"Morag%20Tong%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Morag Tong&lt;/a&gt;. It is &lt;a href=\"Enchant%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;enchanted&lt;/a&gt; to increase the wearer's &lt;a href=\"Short%20Blade%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Short Blade&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Skills%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;.\nEnchantment.\nEnchantment ID: \"sanguine swiftblade_en\"\nAcquisition.\n&lt;a href=\"Threads%20of%20the%20Webspinner\"&gt;Threads of the Webspinner&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Eno%20Hlaalu\"&gt;Eno Hlaalu&lt;/a&gt;, Grandmaster of the Morag Tong requests that twenty-six missing Sanguine items be retrieved for him. This glove is carried by &lt;a href=\"Severa%20Magia\"&gt;Severa Magia&lt;/a&gt; in the lower level of &lt;a href=\"Ald%20Sotha%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Ald Sotha&lt;/a&gt;.\nShe is also targeted for death in the \"&lt;a href=\"Kill%20Severa%20Magia\"&gt;Kill Severa Magia&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"Morag%20Tong%20Quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; performed for Eno Hlaalu."}
