&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"absorb\"&gt;absorb&lt;/a&gt; an adversary's &lt;a href=\"Willpower%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Willpower&lt;/a&gt;. He casts two elemental damage spells, &lt;a href=\"Toxic%20Cloud%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Toxic Cloud&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frost%20Storm\"&gt;Frost Storm&lt;/a&gt; before turning to &lt;a href=\"melee\"&gt;melee&lt;/a&gt; combat. He fights with an &lt;a href=\"Enchant%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;enchanted&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;short sword&lt;/a&gt; that inflicts &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Damage%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt; damage. Gnaw Tooth will not flee and will keep fighting until he or his opponent is dead."}
