{"id": "25333", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25333", "title": "Goblin Chef", "text": "Goblin Chefs are a type of &lt;a href=\"Goblin%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;goblin&lt;/a&gt; in . They are exactly the same as their standard goblin counterparts apart from the chef's hat they wear. They will always flee from the &lt;a href=\"Hero%20of%20Kvatch\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt;, and carry ingredients instead of &lt;a href=\"Lockpick%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;lockpicks&lt;/a&gt;. Cooked &lt;a href=\"Rat%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;rats&lt;/a&gt; are often found above a fire somewhere near to the goblin chef. They usually focus on making the Goblins' signature food - &lt;a href=\"Rat%20Meat%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Rat Meat&lt;/a&gt;."}
