{"id": "942729", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=942729", "title": "Goblin Handler", "text": "Goblin Handler is a high ranked goblin of &lt;a href=\"Mournhold%20%28Tribunal%29\"&gt;Mournhold&lt;/a&gt; found in .\nCombat.\nThe Goblin Handler has a unique claw-type weapon and swings and scratches it towards its enemy, but it is non-lootable.\nEquipment.\nGoblin Handlers wear metal shoulder-guards on their left shoulder, as well as a human skull on the right."}
