{"id": "19326", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19326", "title": "Goblin Totem Staff", "text": "The Goblin Totem Staff is a &lt;a href=\"Staves%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt; often wielded by &lt;a href=\"Goblin%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;goblin&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Goblin%20Shaman\"&gt;shamans&lt;/a&gt;. There are actually several different Goblin Totem Staves, with each goblin tribe possessing one.\nCultural significance.\nEach staff is highly prized by its clan and if it is taken, (by an enemy clan, for instance), they will go to great lengths to retrieve it, often attacking anyone found on the way. As there are many different types of Goblin Totem Staffs, the enchantment specifications may vary.\nLocations.\nThe Goblin Totem Staff is usually wielded by the &lt;a href=\"Goblin%20Shaman\"&gt;Goblin Shaman&lt;/a&gt; of the tribe. Occasionally, it will be found on the ground or propped against something in the clan's current cave. The different goblin tribes are located at:"}
