{"id": "17970", "revid": "25646820", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17970", "title": "Goblin Trouble", "text": "Goblin Trouble is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in . Find &lt;a href=\"Barthel%20Gernand\"&gt;Barthel Gernand&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Crestbridge%20Camp\"&gt;Crestbridge Camp&lt;/a&gt;. He and his family wish to build a settlement at &lt;a href=\"Cropsford%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Cropsford&lt;/a&gt;, but have been unable to do so due to two warring clans of &lt;a href=\"Goblin%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Goblins&lt;/a&gt;.\nMirisa.\nTalk to &lt;a href=\"Mirisa%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Mirisa&lt;/a&gt; to get the next part of this quest. She\u00a0says that the goblins at Cropsford are war parties from &lt;a href=\"Cracked%20Wood%20Cave%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Cracked Wood Cave&lt;/a&gt; on their way to attack a rival tribe at Timberscar Cave (appears as &lt;a href=\"Timberscar%20Hollow%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Timberscar Hollow&lt;/a&gt; on the &lt;a href=\"Hero%20of%20Kvatch\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt;'s map). The Timberscar Cave goblins stole the Cracked Wood Cave tribe's Totem Head.\nWalkthrough.\nThere are several ways to finish this quest. The first way is to recover the Totem Head from the goblins in Timberscar Cave, which would stop the war between the two tribes and leave Cropsford in peace. The &lt;a href=\"Hero%20of%20Kvatch\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt; could do this and not have to kill any goblins; sneaking in and stealing the Totem Head. The second way is to kill the shaman of Cracked Wood Cave, which should effectively destroy the tribe and stop their war parties from attacking Cropsford. A third method is to simply kill all of the goblins in one or both caves.\nOnce they either recover the Totem Head or kill the Shaman return to &lt;a href=\"Mirisa%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Mirisa&lt;/a&gt;. If they took the Totem Head she will tell them that they can cause trouble by giving the Totem Head to a rival goblin tribe. Talk to Barthel Gernand to complete the quest. He promises them a hero's welcome in Cropsford once they have had a chance to establish the settlement.\nWhen returning to Cropsford after two weeks, be sure to locate a chest named \"Reward Chest\" on the second floor of &lt;a href=\"Bincals%27%20House\"&gt;Bincals' House&lt;/a&gt; underneath the stair to the third floor. It refills with &lt;a href=\"Septim%20%28Coin%29\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt; periodically which the Hero is free to take."}
