{"id": "71076", "revid": "3254372", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=71076", "title": "Sibbi Black-Briar (Character)", "text": "Sibbi Black-Briar is a &lt;a href=\"Nords%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Nord&lt;/a&gt; residing in the &lt;a href=\"Riften%20Jail\"&gt;Riften Jail&lt;/a&gt;. As the grandson of &lt;a href=\"Maven%20Black-Briar\"&gt;Maven Black-Briar&lt;/a&gt; by her son &lt;a href=\"Hemming%20Black-Briar\"&gt;Hemming&lt;/a&gt;, Sibbi was imprisoned in Riften Jail for eight months, accused of murder. A note from his mother to &lt;a href=\"Anuriel\"&gt;Anuriel&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Jarl\"&gt;Jarl&lt;/a&gt;'s Stewardess, reveals that Maven Black-Briar is grateful for the incarceration. He tasks the &lt;a href=\"Last%20Dragonborn\"&gt;Dragonborn&lt;/a&gt; with finding his ex-fianc\u00e9e, &lt;a href=\"Lynly%20Star-Sung\"&gt;Svidi&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"Promises%20to%20Keep\"&gt;Promises to Keep&lt;/a&gt;.\nAfter obtaining the quest from &lt;a href=\"Louis%20Letrush\"&gt;Louis Letrush&lt;/a&gt;, go to the &lt;a href=\"Riften%20Jail\"&gt;Riften Jail&lt;/a&gt; and either persuade the jail guard to give access or bribe him with gold. During a conversation with Sibbi, he will say that the horse wasn't actually his, but belongs to his family, and will tell where to retrieve the papers, which are at the Black-Briar Lodge.\n&lt;a href=\"The%20Lover%27s%20Requital\"&gt;The Lover's Requital&lt;/a&gt;.\nIf the Dragonborn speaks to Sibbi about the reason he is in jail, he will ask for help to find the location of the woman who got him incarcerated and this unmarked &lt;a href=\"Miscellaneous%20Quests%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;miscellaneous quest&lt;/a&gt; related to &lt;a href=\"Ivarstead%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Ivarstead&lt;/a&gt; will start. When returning to Sibbi, he hands over his key to his chest as a reward, Sibbi's Chest Key, which is located in the &lt;a href=\"Black-Briar%20Meadery\"&gt;Black-Briar Meadery&lt;/a&gt;. Any content is free to take."}
