{"id": "25799", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25799", "title": "Sibylla Draconis", "text": "Sibylla Draconis is the youngest member of the &lt;a href=\"Imperials%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Imperial&lt;/a&gt; Draconis Family. The &lt;a href=\"Hero%20of%20Kvatch\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt; needs to kill her and her family to complete &lt;a href=\"Next%20of%20Kin%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;the quest&lt;/a&gt; handed to them in the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Brotherhood%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Dark Brotherhood&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=\"Lucien%20Lachance%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Lucien Lachance&lt;/a&gt; to receive 500 .\nAs noted by her mother, &lt;a href=\"Perennia%20Draconis\"&gt;Perennia Draconis&lt;/a&gt;, in the &lt;a href=\"Draconis%20Gift%20List\"&gt;shopping list&lt;/a&gt; that she gives the Hero (or that they take from Perennia's corpse), Sibylla is a 'feral' woman. Indeed, she lives amongst &lt;a href=\"Wolf%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;wolves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Bear%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;bears&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Mountain%20Lion%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;mountain lions&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Muck%20Valley%20Cavern%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Muck Valley Cavern&lt;/a&gt; and immediately becomes hostile when she sees the Hero.\nShe is found either near the entrance of her cave or near her bedroll/fire pit area. She wears a huntsman vest and huntsman loincloth and fights hand-to-hand or with a mace. Her mother pays the Hero to buy her a nice, warm blanket.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"Next%20of%20Kin%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Next of Kin&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe objective given through the &lt;a href=\"Dead%20Drop%20Orders%202\"&gt;Dead Drop Orders 2&lt;/a&gt;, is to eliminate the entire Draconis family, five targets in total. The only information given at the start of the mission is the location of &lt;a href=\"Perennia%20Draconis\"&gt;Perennia Draconis&lt;/a&gt;, the mother of the family. She is located at &lt;a href=\"Applewatch%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Applewatch&lt;/a&gt; farm just west of &lt;a href=\"Bruma%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Bruma&lt;/a&gt;. The aforementioned shopping list then given by her mother reveals the locations of the other family members."}
