{"id": "17104", "revid": "5064773", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17104", "title": "Side Quests (Oblivion)", "text": "&lt;a href=\"Cyrodiil\"&gt;Cyrodiil&lt;/a&gt; contains many side quests that do not pertain to a particular &lt;a href=\"Factions%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;faction&lt;/a&gt; or affect the &lt;a href=\"Main%20Quest%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Main Quest&lt;/a&gt;. These quests are often heard through rumors, found by simply talking to the right &lt;a href=\"Characters%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt;, or simply by reading an article or finding an item, such as the quest \"&lt;a href=\"Seeking%20Your%20Roots\"&gt;Seeking Your Roots&lt;/a&gt;.\" This article lists quests by \"starting\" &lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt;.\nSee for an alphabetical listing of all side quests.\nImperial City Quests.\nWalkthroughs of quests which start in the &lt;a href=\"Imperial%20City\"&gt;Imperial City&lt;/a&gt;, sorted by district."}
{"id": "818198", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=818198", "title": "Side Quests (Online)", "text": "Side Quests are &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quests&lt;/a&gt; in that are self-contained stories not related to other narratives and stories. Some side quests may form part of a minor narrative where one side quest carries on from another. All &lt;a href=\"zones\"&gt;zones&lt;/a&gt; have many side quests that can be found in various locations for different contexts, such as those for &lt;a href=\"delves\"&gt;delves&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"public%20dungeons\"&gt;public dungeons&lt;/a&gt;. Most &lt;a href=\"points%20of%20interest\"&gt;points of interest&lt;/a&gt; in a zone have an associated side quest or quests that, upon completing the quest or series of quests, marks the location as completed."}
