{"id": "901533", "revid": "26459635", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=901533", "title": "Siege Commander Dulph", "text": "Siege Commander Dulph is an &lt;a href=\"Orsimer%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Orsimer&lt;/a&gt; found at the siege camp just outside &lt;a href=\"Frostbreak%20Fortress\"&gt;Frostbreak Fortress&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Wrothgar%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Wrothgar&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"The%20Hidden%20Harvest\"&gt;The Hidden Harvest&lt;/a&gt;.\nSiege Commander Dulph will ask the Vestige to help &lt;a href=\"Eveli%20Sharp-Arrow\"&gt;Eveli Sharp-Arrow&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Alinon%20the%20Alchemist\"&gt;Alinon the Alchemist&lt;/a&gt; deal with the &lt;a href=\"Harpy%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Harpies&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Forsworn%20Briarheart\"&gt;Forsworn Briarheart&lt;/a&gt;s, respectively.\nDialogue.\n\"You... You brought the king here? Then welcome to our siege camp. Sorry you had to see those damn harpies at work. I'm not sure King Kurog should be walking around in the open, but I've got a barrel full of my own worries to deal with.\"\nConversations.\nWhen approaching him:\nSiege Commander Dulph: \"If you don't find the alchemist and destroy those nests, we'll never break this siege!\"\nCaptain Gorrath: \"You heard him! For the king!\"\nSiege Commander Dulph: \"Get down!\"\n&lt;A harpy snatches Captain Gorrath&gt;\nCaptain Gorrath: \"No! No! Let me go!\"\nSiege Commander Dulph: \"Damn it! I lose more soldiers that way!\"\nKing Kurog: \"Looks like General Dulph could use a hand.\""}
