{"id": "25031", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25031", "title": "Sigilium Sanguis", "text": "The Sigilium Sanguis are rooms located at the top of the main towers of &lt;a href=\"Mehrunes%20Dagon\"&gt;Mehrunes Dagon's&lt;/a&gt; planes of &lt;a href=\"Oblivion%20%28Realm%29\"&gt;Oblivion&lt;/a&gt;. Their primary use is to keep the &lt;a href=\"Sigil%20Stone%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Sigil Stones&lt;/a&gt; that maintain the portals between Oblivion and &lt;a href=\"Mundus\"&gt;Mundus&lt;/a&gt;. Removal of the Sigil Stone at the center of the room will cause that portal to close permanently."}
