{"id": "1000818", "revid": "26459635", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1000818", "title": "The Champion Division", "text": "The Champion Division is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in .\nBackground.\n\"I have defeated the champions of the three major divisions in Thizzrini Arena. Now I am ready to face Ishalga and become the Grand Champion of Thizzrini Arena.\"\nWalkthrough.\n&lt;a href=\"Feluni\"&gt;Feluni&lt;/a&gt; informs the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; that the only one left to challenge is the &lt;a href=\"Ishalga\"&gt;Grand Champion&lt;/a&gt; of the arena. She warns, however, that the Grand Champion gets to set the rules of the tournament should someone challenge her.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; approach &lt;a href=\"Ishalga\"&gt;Ishalga&lt;/a&gt;, who has taken notice of your successes and says she looks forward to ending your winning streak. You officially challenge her reign as champion. Since she gets to set the rules, she informs the Vestige of some &lt;a href=\"skooma\"&gt;skooma&lt;/a&gt; in Feluni's office and requires that the Vestige steal it.\u00a0\nUpon entering her office building and going downstairs, the Vestige is attacked by thugs sent by Ishalga. Defeat them and get the skooma off Feluni's desk and return. Ishalga seems surprised that the Vestige is back. They retort that her thugs were surprised as well. She takes offense at the implication that she was involved and says she will see them in the arena.\nIn the arena Ishalga is the only contender. She will use magic to pull the Vestige towards her and immobilize them. The floor traps work but it is difficult to get her to follow. Having both ranged and close attacks is useful."}
