{"id": "18292", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=18292", "title": "The Count's Arms", "text": "The Count's Arms is the &lt;a href=\"Taverns%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;tavern&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Anvil%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Anvil&lt;/a&gt; run by &lt;a href=\"Wilbur\"&gt;Wilbur&lt;/a&gt;. Located between &lt;a href=\"Quill-Weave\"&gt;Quill Weave's&lt;/a&gt; House and &lt;a href=\"Arvena%20Thelas\"&gt;Arvena Thelas&lt;/a&gt;' &lt;a href=\"Arvena%20Thelas%27%20House\"&gt;House&lt;/a&gt;, it is in view when entering from the Anvil Dock Gate. One can enter the inn from the front or a back door near the city wall.\nThe ground floor is dominated by a spacious taproom and \"The Count's Arms Private Rooms\", upstairs, has five bedrooms.\nRegular customers include: &lt;a href=\"Quill-Weave\"&gt;Quill-Weave&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Jesan%20Sextius\"&gt;Jesan Sextius&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Mandil\"&gt;Mandil&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Didier%20Aumilie\"&gt;Didier Aumilie&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Velwyn%20Benirus\"&gt;Velwyn Benirus&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Wilbur\"&gt;Wilbur&lt;/a&gt; sells only foodstuffs and it costs 25 to stay one night.\nQuests.\n&lt;a href=\"Where%20Spirits%20Have%20Lease\"&gt;Where Spirits Have Lease&lt;/a&gt;.\nRumor around in Anvil has it that &lt;a href=\"Velwyn%20Benirus\"&gt;Velwyn Benirus&lt;/a&gt; is selling &lt;a href=\"Benirus%20Manor\"&gt;Benirus Manor&lt;/a&gt; for 5,000 ."}
