{"id": "866352", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=866352", "title": "The Covenant Infiltrator", "text": "The Covenant Infiltrator is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in .\nBackground.\n\"I've encountered a Covenant scout named Damrina in Razak's Wheel. She was captured by Imperials and has asked for my aid.\"\nWalkthrough.\nWithin &lt;a href=\"Razak%27s%20Wheel\"&gt;Razak's Wheel&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; comes across Damrina, a Covenant scout who has been captured by the forces of the &lt;a href=\"Seventh%20Legion%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Seventh Legion&lt;/a&gt;. Upon being freed, the Vestige is told that Damrina covered important patrol orders, and is tasked with retrieving them and killing Damrina's interrogators.\nUpon returning with the orders, and killing the interrogators, Damrina rewards the Vestige with gold and thanks them for their aid."}
