{"id": "878076", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=878076", "title": "The Crocodiles' Many Tears", "text": "The Crocodiles' Many Tears is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Online%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; available in .\nBackground.\n\"A young Redguard named Raiyeem was traveling through the Fallen Grotto when a crocodile wounded him fatally. His final wish was for me to prevent a similar fate from befalling his brother. I should slay the crocodiles and take their meat.\""}
